a=\\\"false\\\"\\u003e\\n\\u003cul start=\\\"1\\\" class=\\\"list-bullet1\\\"\\u003e\\n\\u003cli class=\\\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UE7Pd3MdRoV6TOxqZk9cvK6inse\\\" data-list=\\\"bullet\\\"\\u003e\\n\\u003cdiv\\u003e\\n\\u003cstrong\\u003eAdaptive Ultra-Comfort:\\u003c\\/strong\\u003e Designed to relieve in-ear discomfort, soundcore AeroClip open-ear clip-on earbuds let you enjoy music pressure-free for every outdoor venture.\\u003c\\/div\\u003e\\n\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli class=\\\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CBrTdhu3aoc41bxpqXOcfGEAnjb\\\" data-list=\\\"bullet\\\"\\u003e\\n\\u003cdiv\\u003e\\n\\u003cstrong\\u003eFlexible, Secure Fit:\\u003c\\/strong\\u003e soundcore AeroClip clip-on earbuds boast an adaptive open-ring design that endures 20,000 bends. Feather-light and flexible, they stay secure for all-day wear.\\u003c\\/div\\u003e\\n\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli class=\\\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EIGLdr7TGowTzdxZHk6cWyrjnqg\\\" data-list=\\\"bullet\\\"\\u003e\\n\\u003cdiv\\u003e\\n\\u003cstrong\\u003eClearer \\u003c\\/strong\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003eAudio\\u003c\\/strong\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003e, Richer Bass: \\u003c\\/strong\\u003eEnjoy ultra-clear, rich bass sound with in-ear-level quality. Our advanced virtual bass technology enriches the lows, complemented by a 12mm*12mm titanium-coated driver for clear listening.\\u003c\\/div\\u003e\\n\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli class=\\\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ASAKdP1UfoTJH4xusUncHI1ynHe\\\" data-list=\\\"bullet\\\"\\u003e\\n\\u003cdiv\\u003e\\n\\u003cstrong\\u003eAI-Boosted Clear Calls:\\u003c\\/strong\\u003e With 4 beamforming mics, wind-blocking meshes, and advanced AI, experience flawless calls, even in the busiest \\u003cmeta charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"\\u003e\\n\\u003cspan\\u003estreet\\u003c\\/span\\u003e.\\u003c\\/div\\u003e\\n\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli class=\\\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JPEhdoSOEoxW7axvQSQcNWLtnxg\\\" data-list=\\\"bullet\\\"\\u003e\\n\\u003cdiv\\u003