003eIncredible Endurance\\u003c\\/b\\u003e: Get 9 hours of intense listening from a single charge and boost that to 36 hours with the included charging case. That’s up to 5 weeks of workouts on a single charge.\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003e\\n\\u003cb\\u003eEffortless Comfort\\u003c\\/b\\u003e: True wireless earbuds with extra-flex ear tips and hooks ensure a free, satisfying, and invincible fit, no matter how hardcore your workout. Comes with an extensive selection of tips and wings for tailored listening.\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003e\\n\\u003cb\\u003eClear Calls\\u003c\\/b\\u003e: cVc 8.0 noise reduction effectively isolates your voice while removing background noise. You’re heard clearly from any location.\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003e\\n\\u003cb\\u003eBetter Bluetooth\\u003c\\/b\\u003e: Qualcomm aptX audio technology delivers exceptional, lossless sound quality over your Bluetooth connection.\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003c\\/ul\\u003e\",\"published_at\":\"2026-03-12T02:55:46-07:00\",\"created_at\":\"2021-08-18T20:57:17-07:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-17T06:35:36-07:00\",\"vendor\":\"soundcoreusa\",\"product_type\":\"headphone\",\"tags\":[\"BassUp technology\",\"kelong\",\"Noise Reduction\",\"Playtime: 9 Hours\",\"Spirit Series\",\"Sports \\u0026 Exercise\",\"Waterproof\"],\"variants\":[{\"id\":40445184278718,\"title\":\"Black\",\"option1\":\"Black\",\"option2\":null,\"option3\":null,\"sku\":\"A3918011-F0\",\"requires_shipping\":true,\"taxable\":true,\"featured_image\":{\"id\":29599027757246,\"product_id\":6911560810686,\"position\":1,\"created_at\":\"2021-08-18T20:57:21-07:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2021-08-18T20:57:21-07:00\",\"alt\":null,\"width\":960,\"height\":960,\"src\":\"https:\\/\\/cdn.shopify.com\\/s\\/files\\/1\\/0516\\/3761\\/6830\\/products\\/A3918011_3a157750-d8b8-47f8-b366-dfff77816dff.jpg?v=1629345441\",\"variant_ids\":[40445184278718]},\"available\":false,\"price\":\"9999999.99\",\"grams\":128,\"compare_at_price\":null,\"positi