\"width\":2400,\"height\":2400}],\"options\":[{\"name\":\"Color\",\"position\":1,\"values\":[\"Sky Blue\"]}]},{\"id\":7611849113790,\"title\":\"soundcore Motion X600 | High-Quality Sound Wireless Speaker\",\"handle\":\"motion-x600-a3130011\",\"body_html\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003e\\u003cmeta charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"\\u003e\\n\\u003ca href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.soundcore.com\\/corporate-purchase\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan data-eleid=\\\"5\\\" style=\\\"color: #17bbef;\\\" class=\\\"text-only\\\"\\u003eBulk Buying, Big Savings! Click Now \\u0026amp; Know More \\u0026gt;\\u0026gt;\\u0026gt;\\u0026gt;\\u0026gt;\\u003c\\/span\\u003e\\u003c\\/a\\u003e\\u003c\\/strong\\u003e\\u003c\\/span\\u003e\\u003c\\/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cul class=\\\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\\\"\\u003e\\n\\u003cli class=\\\"a-spacing-mini\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003eImmersive Spatial Audio:\\u003c\\/strong\\u003e Inspired by theater acoustics, Motion X600 features an upward-firing full-range driver on top, combined with 2 woofers and 2 tweeters on each side to deliver sound all around you.\\u003c\\/span\\u003e\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli class=\\\"a-spacing-mini\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003eTransform Any Room Into a Live Venue: \\u003c\\/strong\\u003eMotion X600's goes beyond the boundaries of traditional speakers, offering a multidimensional experience that resonates with vibrancy and detail. Feel like you're in the room with your favorite artist, every time you press play.\\u003c\\/span\\u003e\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli class=\\\"a-spacing-mini\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003e50W Room-Filling Sound: \\u003c\\/strong\\u003eWhether you're having a party or just enjoying your favorite tunes, the 50W sound will fill any space with rich, high-quality sound that brings music to life.\\u003c\\/span\\u003e\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli class=\\\"a-spacing-mini\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003eTake Immersive Music Anywhere:\\u003c\\/strong\\u003e Portable and lightweight, Motion X600 is easy to carry between rooms to transform any part of your home into an immersive listening space.\\u003c\\/span\\u003e\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli class=\\\"a-spacing-mini\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003e12-Hour Playtime:\\u003c\\/strong\\u003e Keep listening to music and podcasts for days at a time—with zero battery anxiety.\\u003c\\/span\\u003e\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli class=\\\"a-spacing-mini\\\"\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003eFully Waterproof:\\u003c\\/strong\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003e \\u003c\\/span\\u003eFeatures IPX7 waterproof protection so you can simply relax and listen without worrying about the speaker getting wet.\\u003c\\/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eNote: For peak performance, please use the soundcore app and update to the latest firmware.\\u003c\\/p\\u003e\\n\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003c\\/ul\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003c!----\\u003e\\u003c\\/p\\u003e\",\"published_at\":\"2026-03-12T02:54:53-07:00\",\"created_at\":\"2023-05-07T20:53:51-07:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-17T06:35:36-07:00\",\"vendor\":\"soundcoreusa\",\"product_type\":\"speaker\",\"tags\":[\"akr_product_discount_tag\",\"fall-pd\",\"full\",\"fullprice\",\"High-Fidelity\",\"Home\",\"Home Office\",\"Motion Series\",\"soundcore_xmas_sale_2312\",\"Spatial Audio\",\"Waterproof\"],\"variants\":[{\"id\":44256434716862,\"title\":\"Lunar Blue\",\"option1\":\"Lunar Blue\",\"option2\":null,\"option3\":null,\"sku\":\"A3130031\",\"requires_shipping\":true,\"taxable\":true,\"featured_image\":{\"id\":38745566707902,\"product_id\":7611849113790,\"position\":8,\"created_at\":\"2025-07-03T03:27:51-07:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2025-07-09T05:14:23-07:00\",\"alt\":\"soundcore home speaker with spatial audio and sleek blue design\",\"width\":1800,\"height\":1800,\"src\":\"https:\\/\\/cdn.shopify.com\\/s\\/files\\/1\\/0516\\/3761\\/6830\\/files\\/A313061-Motion_X600-2000x2000-01.png?v=17520