 Audio for Restful Sleep: \\u003c\\/strong\\u003eBinaural beats deliver different frequencies to each ear, which helps sync your brainwaves with calming patterns to promote relaxation and restful sleep.\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003e\\n\\u003cmeta charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"\\u003e \\u003cstrong\\u003eAll-Night Comfort for Side Sleeping: \\u003c\\/strong\\u003eBoasts ultra-soft silicone, short nozzles, and a lightweight, slim profile to relieve pressure for side sleeping Using 3D mapping of thousands of ear canals, it's ergonomically shaped to fit most ears comfortably.\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003e\\n\\u003cmeta charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"\\u003e \\u003cstrong\\u003eYour Custom Sleep Solution: \\u003c\\/strong\\u003ePersonalize your bedtime audio, sleep reminders, built-in alarms, and more with an easy, all-in-one setup for a restful night--just the way you like it.\\u003c\\/li\\u003e\\n\\u003c\\/ul\\u003e\",\"published_at\":\"2026-03-12T02:53:31-07:00\",\"created_at\":\"2025-10-16T04:27:44-07:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-17T06:35:36-07:00\",\"vendor\":\"soundcoreusa\",\"product_type\":\"\",\"tags\":[\"code not applied\",\"kelong\"],\"variants\":[{\"id\":45480323186878,\"title\":\"Moonlit White\",\"option1\":\"Moonlit White\",\"option2\":null,\"option3\":null,\"sku\":\"D1301Z21\",\"requires_shipping\":true,\"taxable\":true,\"featured_image\":{\"id\":39368602124478,\"product_id\":8597335474366,\"position\":1,\"created_at\":\"2025-09-04T03:14:27-07:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2025-09-04T03:15:07-07:00\",\"alt\":\"soundcore sleep earbuds with ZDNET recommends label\",\"width\":1608,\"height\":1608,\"src\":\"https:\\/\\/cdn.shopify.com\\/s\\/files\\/1\\/0516\\/3761\\/6830\\/files\\/D1301Z21_Rich_image_TD01_US_V1_9c394dde-044a-4ef1-8323-246fa77e5a51.png?v=1756980907\",\"variant_ids\":[45480323186878]},\"available\":true,\"price\":\"183.99\",\"grams\":259,\"compare_at_price\":\"229.99\",\"position\":1,\"product_id\":8597335474366,\"created_at\":\"2025-10-16T04:27:45-07:00\